title: Luis Fonsi - Despacito [Spanish Karaoke] CDG+MP3
description:
This is the UK number 1 in it's original form without JB which perhaps is a good thing hi...

NOTE as any non English song is only entered once, that is only one version, the Title string does not give Karaoke Label info, but does give the language making it simple for the Karaoke Host to find and list ALL French, Spanish, Swedish, Maltese, German or Italian language songs and then scroll down to find the artist or title.

All Rigmar Karaoke is tagged and titled following best industry practice for MUSIC files:

Artist - Song Title [any other information]

This recommended method applies to Audio and Music Video files as well so when searching for a song, professional playout software can give very good results.

Audio is 320 kbps at 41000 Hz.  Included is a plain text file with updates on the Rigmar Collection 2017 which I will be stopping seeding at the end of JUNE 2017 to recover the disk space from my seedboxes.
